<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">📁 <strong>New Folder</strong> icon</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Click those to create files/folders <strong>inside</strong> your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">part-4-ai-solution-design</code> folder directly. No need to go to Desktop.</p>
