n class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Part 4: AI Solution Design — Agentic AI in Finance</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Overview</span><span>
</span></span><span>This project presents an AI solution design for applying Agentic AI in the Finance domain.
</span><span>It covers problem definition, data requirements, model selection, evaluation, and responsible AI considerations.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Domain</span><span>
</span></span><span>Finance
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Problem</span><span>
</span></span><span>Financial institutions rely on slow, manual processes for fraud detection, loan approvals,
</span><span>portfolio management, and customer support. This project proposes an Agentic AI system
</span><span>that can autonomously handle these tasks in real time.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Files</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`solution_report.md`</span><span> — Full solution report covering all 8 tasks
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`diagrams/solution_architecture.png`</span><span> — System architecture diagram
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`ai_usecase_reference_catalog.csv`</span><span> — Reference catalog used for domain selection
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`business_kpi_sample.csv`</span><span> — KPI reference used for business impact analysis
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`data_dictionary__2_.md`</span><span> — Data dictionary for reference files
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Author</span><span>
</span></span><span>Your Name — Masai School</span></code></pre></div></div>
