n class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Agentic AI Solution Architecture — Finance</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> System Flow</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">```</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block">+------------------+
</span></span><span>|   Data Sources   |
</span><span>|------------------|
</span><span>| - Bank Database  |
</span><span>| - Stock Market   |
</span><span>| - Customer Logs  |
</span><span>| - Credit Bureau  |
