</span><span>| - Feature Eng.   |
</span><span>| - Normalization  |
</span><span>+--------+---------+
</span><span>         |
</span><span>         v
</span><span>+------------------+
</span><span>|   AI Models      |
</span><span>|------------------|
</span><span>| - FFNN (Fraud)   |
</span><span>| - LSTM (Market)  |
</span><span>| - BERT (Text)    |
</span><span>| - RL Agent       |
</span><span>+--------+---------+
</span><span>         |
</span><span>         v
</span><span>+------------------+
</span><span>|  Agentic Layer   |
</span><span>|------------------|
</span><span>| - Plan &amp; Decide  |
</span><span>| - Act &amp; Execute  |
</span><span>| - Human Oversight|
</span><span>+--------+---------+
</span><span>         |
</span><span>         v
</span><span>+------------------+
